name: Tm4c123gxl
tagline: All the current labs I've done for the edx course on embedded systems taught by Professors Valvano and Yerraballi.
body:
### Welcome to my TM4C123GXL Repo.
I used the code in this repo for the online class, _UT.6.02x Embedded Systems - Shape the World_, hosted at edx.org.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
